        <item>
            <title>1.1.8</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 14:56:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/gangz1o/Clipaste</link>
            <sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>https://github.com/gangz1o/Clipaste/releases/tag/v1.1.8</sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>
            <sparkle:version>10108</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### ✨ 本次更新

🎨 优化

- 优化盲打搜索输入链路，现已更好支持中文输入法首字符拼音组合，以及 `Shift + 字母` 的大写输入
- 优化菜单栏图标交互：左键点击直接打开剪贴板面板，右键点击继续显示菜单

---

### ✨ What's New

🎨 Improvements

- Improved the type-to-search input flow with better support for first-character IME composition and uppercase input via `Shift + letter`
- Improved the menu bar icon behavior: left click now opens the clipboard panel directly, while right click continues to show the menu

]]></description>
