        <item>
            <title>1.1.7</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 14:51:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/gangz1o/Clipaste</link>
            <sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>https://github.com/gangz1o/Clipaste/releases/tag/v1.1.7</sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>
            <sparkle:version>10107</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[✨ 本次更新

🎨 优化

- 优化 Excel / WPS 富文本复制保真，尽可能保留表格边框与原始格式
- 优化混合剪贴板识别策略，优先保留文本与富文本内容，减少被错误识别为图片的情况
- 优化设置页侧边栏激活色管理，改为语义化颜色资产，便于后续统一调整主题风格

---

✨ What's New

🎨 Improvements

- Improved rich text fidelity for Excel / WPS copies to better preserve table borders and original formatting
- Improved mixed clipboard detection to better preserve text and rich text content instead of capturing them as images
- Improved settings sidebar active color management by moving it to semantic color assets for easier theme maintenance

]]></description>
